    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Mesh independence, experimental validation against FDA pump data, and turbulence model sensitivity analyses collectively support the claim that the CFD model reliably identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is met at the identified worst-case operating point. The credibility assessment is accepted for submission to regulatory review.",
